headline: Q4 Rundown: Simply Good Foods (NASDAQ:SMPL) Vs Other Shelf-Stable Food Stocks
summary: The end of the earnings season is always a good time to take a step back and see who shined (and who not so much). Let’s take a look at how shelf-stable food stocks fared in Q4, starting with Simply Good Foods (NASDAQ:SMPL).
